        Median vs Average Property Prices in Brisbane: What the Difference Means for Sellers
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        When agents and the media quote Brisbane property prices, they almost always cite the median. Here is what that number actually means, what it does not tell you, and how to use it correctly.
      </p>
